text: Horst is a municipality of the district of Steinburg, in Schleswig-Holstein, Germany. As of 31 December 2018, 5,709 people lived there. It is about 14 km southeast of Itzehoe, and 7 km northwest of Elmshorn. Category:Municipalities in Schleswig-Holstein Category:Steinburg (district)
title: Horst, Steinburg
